column2: "You're amazin'. The difference between us is so huge, I can't even be jealous of ya any more."
"I could kinda deal with 60. Even 65, if I really pushed myself."
"But when I saw how ya handled 70 of those guys so easily, it really shook me how confident you were."
"But cometh the hour, cometh the man. It's time I lived up to your example. Just you watch me go, killer!"
